hey [~scottb] one more - I notice that our bash command in the docs do not match the one in the current FastStart:

in FastStart - 
{code}$> bash <(curl -Ls eucalyptus.com/install){code}

in the Install Guide - 
{code}bash <(curl -Ls https://www.eucalyptus.com/install){code}

I'm guessing the latter is a cut/paste thing with one of our tools that added the https:// ..?
